《'''美麗公主'''》（{{lang-it|La Bella Principessa}}）是一幅疑似由[[達文西|達文西]]所作的[[肖像畫|肖像畫]]。畫像高33厘米、闊23厘米，以粉筆和油墨畫成，左上角殘留一個懷疑屬於達文西的[[指紋|指紋]]。畫像1998年只以19,000美元成交，如果該畫真屬達文西作品，估計將升值至1.6億美元。<ref>[http://hk.apple.nextmedia.com/template/apple/art_main.php?iss_id=20091014&sec_id=15335&subsec_id=15339&art_id=13310974 指模揭畫作屬達文西真迹 14萬身價升至 12億] {{Wayback|url=http://hk.apple.nextmedia.com/template/apple/art_main.php?iss_id=20091014&sec_id=15335&subsec_id=15339&art_id=13310974 |date=20091016015112 }}蘋果日報</ref>

據英國[[牛津大學|牛津大學]]藝術歷史學院名譽教授[[马丁·坎普_(艺术史家)|马丁·坎普]]推斷，畫中少女應是米蘭公爵[[盧多維科·斯福爾扎|盧多維科·斯福爾扎]]的女兒{{link-it|比安卡·斯福爾扎|Bianca Giovanna Sforza}}。<ref>[http://news.chinatimes.com/2007Cti/2007Cti-News/2007Cti-News-Content/0,4521,110513+112009101400398,00.html 畫作疑留達文西指紋？價值51億] {{webarchive|url=https://web.archive.org/web/20091024180442/http://news.chinatimes.com/2007Cti/2007Cti-News/2007Cti-News-Content/0,4521,110513+112009101400398,00.html |date=2009-10-24 }}中國時報</ref><ref>{{cite news|author=艾米|title=达·芬奇的 “漂亮公主”|url=http://www.chinese.rfi.fr/%E9%AD%85%E5%8A%9B%E6%B3%95%E5%85%B0%E8%A5%BF/20110928-%E8%BE%BE%E2%80%A2%E8%8A%AC%E5%A5%87%E7%9A%84%E7%AC%AC%E5%8D%81%E4%B8%89%E5%BC%A0%E4%BE%A7%E4%BA%BA%E5%A4%B4%E5%83%8F%E4%B9%8B%E8%B0%9C%E7%BB%88%E4%BA%8E%E6%8F%AD%E5%BC%80|newspaper=法广|date=2011年9月28日}}</ref>

2015年11月底，艺术品造假者{{link-en|肖恩·格林哈尔|Shaun Greenhalgh}}在他出版的新书中声称，《美丽公主》并不是达芬奇的作品，而是他在1978年伪造的作品，画中人是他在超市打工时的同事。<ref>{{cite news|title=达·芬奇画作被疑造假 市面估价高达1亿美元|url=http://news.sina.com.cn/o/2015-12-01/doc-ifxmainy1492390.shtml|accessdate=2015-12-01|agency=京华时报|date=2015-12-01|archive-date=2015-12-08|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20151208131600/http://news.sina.com.cn/o/2015-12-01/doc-ifxmainy1492390.shtml|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite news|title=Is this Da Vinci masterpiece really just Sally the shopgirl from Bolton? Prolific forger claims he created the £100m artwork in based on a worker at his local Co-op|url=http://www.dailymail.co.uk/news/article-3338200/Is-Da-Vinci-masterpiece-really-just-Sally-shopgirl-Bolton-Prolific-forger-claims-drew-100m-Renaissance-masterpiece-1970s-based-till-girl-local-op.html|accessdate=2015-12-01|agency=Daily Mail|date=2015-11-29|archive-date=2015-11-30|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20151130061030/http://www.dailymail.co.uk/news/article-3338200/Is-Da-Vinci-masterpiece-really-just-Sally-shopgirl-Bolton-Prolific-forger-claims-drew-100m-Renaissance-masterpiece-1970s-based-till-girl-local-op.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>

